



Solo Blogging platform backend
- a model to store blogs
- model needs to have fields as such: blog title, blog itself, creation date, maybe a slug field, published/draft status (true/false)
- endpoint to list all blogs partially (used to display all articles in a page)
- endpoint to fetch particular blog (gives full article)
- endpoint to create new blog
- endpoint to publish drafted blog
- endpoint to unpublish (go back to draft mode)
- endpoint to edit blog
- endpoint to delete blog